parties: In the Matter of DISCIPLINE OF Quenton I. WHITE.
casebody.head_matter:
In the Matter of DISCIPLINE OF Quenton I. WHITE.
No. D-2958.
Supreme Court of the United States
April 17, 2017.
Quenton I. White, of Nashville, Tennessee, is suspended from the practice of law in this Court and a rule will issue, returnable within 40 days, requiring him to show cause why he should not be disbarred from the practice of law in this Court.
